%define real_name Tie-Scalar-Timeout

Summary: Scalar variables that time out
Name: perl-Tie-Scalar-Timeout
Version: 1.33
Release: 1
License: Artistic/GPL
Group: Applications/CPAN
URL: http://search.cpan.org/dist/Tie-Scalar-Timeout/

